{"tid":218812,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"（魔性多圖game）小小歐巴桑精靈培育箱 Myjipockle","createTime":"2017-04-26T17:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T16:37:08.000Z","uid":85896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"33309a16995bb675225c1a31c4ade4c276099538","tid":218812,"uid":85896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T17:52:45.000Z","msg":"見佢排行榜第一就down嚟玩下<br />\n點知真心膠得嚟又幾得意<br />\n尤其係個bb嗰樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n...<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3a83acV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3a83acV.jpg&h=3a4393e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一開始嗰bb樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Lv.1=一歲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V75kM9Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV75kM9Q.jpg&h=7f58862d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啲嘢食係自己種，基本上放係到一分鐘就有得收成<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/27/014302_b501ada3b71ae76780942541f1823e6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F27%2F014302_b501ada3b71ae76780942541f1823e6c.jpg&h=59b2ebf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同佢玩遊戲賺錢，得兩嗰game<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/27/014413_3e4fb1887184c439b51a2e89024276f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F27%2F014413_3e4fb1887184c439b51a2e89024276f3.jpg&h=a2756d89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有錢就買傢私、藥水(長速長大用)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/848eA9w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F848eA9w.jpg&h=6c2891fd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ww2cOS1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fww2cOS1.jpg&h=41b6fd5e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/27/014550_43b3c6b03a23c9228b0d6dc152e9bab4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F27%2F014550_43b3c6b03a23c9228b0d6dc152e9bab4.jpg&h=a2144f1f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jX1R3rk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjX1R3rk.jpg&h=2793757d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/27/014551_2ff58385c92867e8777ea597d6c29acf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F27%2F014551_2ff58385c92867e8777ea597d6c29acf.jpg&h=2f9ea964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">到咗某歲數就會唔同樣，變咩樣就睇你餵咩比佢食</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0869WS1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0869WS1.jpg&h=52519b32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隻game有繁中、英文、日文語言揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總括而言佢嗰樣係正嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n歡迎加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7e57a402e3a05ac41ef6d632c4cf90e05cf84a","tid":218812,"uid":275524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:37:08.000Z","msg":"難得有心人。"}]}